  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "In a large skillet, heat the olive oil over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the sliced mushrooms and cook until browned, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and chopped onion, cooking for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Stir in cumin, paprika, salt, and pepper.",
    "In a separate bowl, toss the cubed fired bread with a pinch of salt and pepper.",
